|q|<1
\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\dfrac{nq^n}{1-q^n}=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\dfrac{q^n}{(1-q^n)^2}
\dfrac{q^n}{1-q^n}=\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}q^{n(k+1)}
 \begin{array}{|c|}\hline\\ \color{#ff0000}{\large\quad% \sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}{nq^{n} \over 1 - q^{n}} \color{#000000}{\ =\ } \sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}{q^{n} \over \left(1 - q^{n}\right)^{2}} \quad} \\ \\ \hline \end{array} 
